{
  "texts": [
    "1 However, the proliferation and increasing availability of diverse text mining methods presents researchers with a number of challenging questions.",
    "Which method most accurately approximates human coding for a given task?",
    "Can established dictionary methods be relied upon, or should we invest time in understanding complex large language models?",
    "How much can we trust accessible new implementations that require minimal technical knowledge on the part of researchers?",
    "How do our decisions at various analytical stages affect the performance of different methods?"
  ]
}